# Title: UAC Bypass Using IEInstal - File
# Author: Christian Burkard (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2021-08-30
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the pattern of UAC Bypass using IEInstal.exe (UACMe 64)
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.privilege-escalation, attack.t1548.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/file/file_event/file_event_win_uac_bypass_ieinstal.yml

Image="C:\\Program Files\\Internet Explorer\\IEInstal.exe" TargetFilename="*\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\*" TargetFilename="*consent.exe" TargetFilename="C:\\Users\\*"